2:T6fb,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Tidio better than Zendesk AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Tidio scores 7.0 overall while Zendesk AI scores 8.0. Tidio is best for e-commerce and small businesses, while Zendesk AI excels for enterprises and support teams."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Tidio or Zendesk AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Tidio starts at Free and Zendesk AI starts at $55/agent/mo. Tidio offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Tidio to Zendesk AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Tidio and Zendesk AI support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Tidio vs Zendesk AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Tidio holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10. Zendesk AI has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 6/10. Users praise Tidio for easy setup and attractive pricing and Zendesk AI for industry-leading ticket management."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Tidio or Zendesk AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Zendesk AI for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Tidio remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize easy setup and attractive pricing. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-head