8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Tidio and Zendesk AI share a solid foundation of core features including Live Chat, Ai Chatbot, Ticket Management, Analytics. On the other hand, Zendesk AI uniquely offers Knowledge Base and Voice Support, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Tidio holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Zendesk AI scores 8/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Tidio offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Zendesk AI's starting price of $55/agent/mo. Tidio has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Zendesk AI does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
