c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Tidio is best suited for e commerce, small businesses, Shopify stores, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Zendesk AI, meanwhile, shines for enterprises, support teams, omnichannel service, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2013, Tidio describes itself as \"AI chatbot and live chat platform designed for small and mid-size businesses.\" Zendesk AI, established in 2007, positions itself as \"Enterprise customer service platform with AI-powered ticketing and automation.\" With 6 years between them, Zendesk AI brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Tidio offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Zendesk AI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 7.0), more features (10 vs 8). However, this does not mean Tidio is a poor choice — far from it. Tidio excels in its own right, particularly for e commerce and small businesses.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value industry-leading ticket management, go with Zendesk AI. If easy setup and attractive pricing matters more to you, Tidio is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
